- D111-2: Update upsert_pol_market() to accept and store token_id_no
- D111-3: Create _process_market_record() helper, deduplicate async/sync scan logic
- D111-4: Update fetch_active_pol_markets() to return token_id_no
- D111-5: Update _sync_pol_tokens_from_watchlist() to register both YES and NO tokens
- D111-6: Version bumps (orchestrator v1.1.24¡÷v1.1.25, backend v1.1.14¡÷v1.1.15)
